twcore.core.util
Class InterProcessCommunicator

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.util.InterProcessCommunicator

public class InterProcessCommunicator
extends java.lang.Object

Main class of the Inter-process Communication protocol of TWCore, handling routing of messages between bots along specific channels. Also handles channel subscriptions, creation/deletion of channels, and firing of InterProcessEvents.

Author:
harvey
